Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:46.48,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I don't want nobody to get killed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:51.14,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I'll come and get you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:54.24,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I am always ready to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:03:00.22,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}So don't take all of the blame we were all swept away
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:04.07,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Don't take all of the weight. You always do
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:07.77,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}There will always be something you cannot control
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:12.31,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}We will overcome. Your salvation has begun
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:18.10,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}No signs, no lights, such a mess all over
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:20.28,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Don't kill you hopes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:26.23,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}You make me realize who I need
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:28.62,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I'll be there hold on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:30.60,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}They'll change you somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:33.86,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}So where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:36.41,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I'll reach you by dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:41.58,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}The shadows appear，Illusions are born
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:45.55,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}The fallen angels you run with don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:50.16,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}It is our pain that makes us all human after all
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:53.11,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Torn old sepia photographs show
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:54.97,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Our fragile precious world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.09,0:03:58.73,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Must discard it, respond to the call
Comment: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:32.20,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,=================OPC=================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:46.48,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我不願意看到有人被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:51.14,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我將來找尋你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:54.24,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我一直準備與它們抗爭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:03:00.22,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}所以別一個人承擔過錯 我們都在命運的洪流中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:04.07,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}別一個人把重任扛在肩上 你總會這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:07.77,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}人生不定 總會有些事你無法掌控
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:12.31,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}而我們會克服一切 對你的救濟已經開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:18.10,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}生命跡象為零 抬頭不見星光 腳下遍地混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:20.28,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}然而不要扼殺你的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:26.23,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}你讓我察覺到我心底所求之人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:28.62,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我會堅持在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:30.60,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}可曾幾何時你已被他們改變
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:33.86,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}而真正的你今在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:36.41,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我會在黎明前找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:41.58,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}身影浮現 幻影所生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:45.55,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}你所追逐的 你所不了解的墮落天使們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:50.16,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}畢竟我們的痛苦讓我們更像是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:53.11,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}被撕碎的紅褐色的照片上 所映出的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:54.97,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}是我們脆弱的而又美好的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.09,0:03:58.73,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}必須拋棄舊世界 響應使命的召喚
Comment: 0,0:00:00.67,0:00:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================EDJ=================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:17.20,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}馴染めた白　鳥かご隅　鼓動獲たツボミも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:28.34,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}置き去り声　眩めた　記憶の影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:31.38,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I need your blood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.45,0:22:34.13,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}You read love 唱える
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.23,0:22:37.77,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\an1}足掻く　RED LIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:43.73,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}嗅ぎ分けた音と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.79,0:22:46.71,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}こじ開けたReasonが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.87,0:22:49.90,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ただ平行に並ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:22:55.55,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Come and break it down for me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.63,0:22:57.59,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}A river will flow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:23:03.89,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}KEYがない「欲しい」でも　利害鳴る鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.14,0:23:13.99,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}懺悔さえ乾いた ４拍子が　奏でた意図を辿る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:21.14,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}木漏れ日の赤が騒ぐ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.67,0:00:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================EDC=================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:17.20,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不變的蒼白景色 枷鎖般的鳥籠之內 花蕾獲得了新生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:28.34,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}你漸離漸遠的聲音 是我不敢直視的記憶影子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.45,0:22:34.13,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}高呼 {\fnDFHSMincho-W3\fs25}You read love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.23,0:22:37.77,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\an1}不斷掙扎  {\fnDFHSMincho-W3\fs25}RED LIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:43.73,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}感應到的聲音和
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.79,0:22:46.71,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}最終揭開的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.87,0:22:49.90,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}永遠只是不相交的平行線
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:23:03.89,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}無窮無盡的慾望 是鳴響得失的警鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.14,0:23:13.99,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}連懺悔都已枯竭 追尋著四節拍所奏響的意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:21.14,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}樹蔭下的鮮紅之光蠢蠢欲動
